cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with the problem of inferring the interaction profile of agents in an adaptive diffusion network, which involves machine learning and information theory concepts. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also deals with control and optimization aspects of the network, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) categories.
